

                           [help look]
-----------------------=========+=========-----------------------   

Usage: look
       l
       look at <object>
       l <object>
       look <object>
       l at <object>
       look <direction>

  This command will usually give a more detailed description of an 
object/person/monster than the normal short description. Also used
to look at objects in the long description of a room.

Also see:
 lookdir
